column5: Anyone goin out in the morning?
I intend to be on Stoney looking for Crappie.
hopefully the weekend will be one of fishin'!
I've never fished crappie. Do you need a special set up? bait?
WAS gonna hit the upper Credit, but, not sure now with the forecast.  Playin' it by ear....
If ya do shoot me a message, That was the plan for me...
